snippet.title: LOLLIPOP CHAINSAW RePOP RELEASE TRAILER
snippet.description:
The fierce battle between zombie hunter Juliet and the “Dark Purveyors” led by Swan has now begun in order to stop the zombification that has plunged the entire school into chaos and despair!

LOLLIPOP CHAINSAW RePOP is released today!
